text: Benjamin Isaac Diskin (born August 25, 1982) is an American actor. He is known for his roles as Junior Healy in the USA Network animated series Problem Child, Eugene in Hey Arnold!, Numbuh 1 and Numbuh 2 in Codename: Kids Next Door, Venom/Eddie Brock in The Spectacular Spider-Man, Hahn in Avatar: The Last Airbender, M'comm M'orzz/Ma'alefa'ak in Young Justice and Gonzo and Rizzo in the 2018 revival of Muppet Babies. ==Other websites== * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Los Angeles County, California Category:American movie actors Category:American voice actors
